--------------------------
Bulb Buster
--------------------------

This is a game inspired from a similar game in old atari consoles. The objective is to burst all the bulbs using the CFLs.

-------------
How to use
-------------

1. Install the game by double clicking.
2. Start the game by doble clicking on the game icon.
3. 
4. Press 'close' icon to exit at any moment.

